Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.00,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.89,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you just standin' there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:53.84,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.94,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Rikko, how about openin' the door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:00.39,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.81,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.73,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ritsuko-chan isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:15.95,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.67,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I love the cakes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:20.20,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Do you come here often too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:20.98,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:23.29,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This is Jun-niichan's family's shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:25.36,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.25,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.13,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Yurika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.72,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, why don't you come over \N to my place to watch the jazz practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:35.63,ED-Romaji,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.75\bord0\shad0\fscx41.25\fscy55\pos(304,145)}Shirayuri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:35.63,ED-Romaji,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.75\bord0\shad0\fscx38.75\fscy55\pos(990,145)}Shirayuri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:44.44,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's over. She hates me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.81,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,That avant-garde?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:47.89,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:49.32,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Get your head on straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:51.20,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,How we gonna have a session?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.65,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, Yurika-san is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:57.06,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:59.69,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't your dad tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:01.57,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,that outsiders aren't allowed down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:05.07,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika-san is our friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.06,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm sure Dad wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:09.68,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Yurika-san, enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:10.50,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.75,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kaoru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:16.24,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to get a little fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:22.35,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:34.20,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.58,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's Bon-niichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.56,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro's sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:41.24,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sachiko-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.04,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you playing by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:43.94,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:46.74,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,All my friends are off at cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.31,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.96,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about we play together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:53.64,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.79,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.33,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,It's not playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:00.59,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:07.10,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,This thing's a relic, so it gets ornery sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.96,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:10.78,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,you have to work a little magic on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:17.18,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Jun-nii.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:18.61,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,How'd that get it working?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:21.07,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:25.15,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, is this the Children's \N Telephone Counseling Office?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.99,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:28.86,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,See,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:30.90,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,there's this boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:33.63,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hashiguchi-kun, who's always mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:37.13,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,He hides my indoor shoes and pulls my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.53,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.78,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.50,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:48.93,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,maybe Hashiguchi-kun likes you, Sachiko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:54.36,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is he wants to be friends with you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:56.78,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but doesn't know how to express his feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:59.17,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,so he acts out like that \N without really thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.44,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,He does not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:07.45,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, I made the girl that I really like cry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.22,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to apologize to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:12.71,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but even if I do, I don't think she'll forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:17.71,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:21.71,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,That was my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.17,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:32.78,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:37.52,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.90,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:47.16,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Coincidentally, I've been \N going to the shop for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:50.08,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea it was your family's.
