Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.29,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,The coincidences keep on coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:58.29,Default,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Even the name is similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:09.23,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's someone that I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:10.79,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:13.22,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,he's the only one I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:16.55,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flattered by the way you feel about me, Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.60,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flattered, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.80,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:36.44,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:37.61,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.27,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.11,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You seem kinda troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:43.00,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Here, eat this an' cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.41,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:50.18,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I said something terrible to Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:54.15,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san might not come back here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.71,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.12,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sachiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:06.92,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:09.84,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...know who Rikko li—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:11.95,Default,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:14.06,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.09,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:17.73,Default,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,School starts again today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.66,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I can't ask.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:25.46,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's impossible to talk about \N romantic stuff here in this house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.97,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon! It's been too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:32.18,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you come over for \N practice during winter vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.30,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:45.32,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... The teacher told me to give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.32,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.59,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad's finally come back,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:08.76,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but everything seems so bleak right now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.59,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that I can't bring myself to talk about anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.52,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:24.96,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen... What are you doing out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.45,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon! Move for a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.53,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon, get a jacket on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.19,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:38.64,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:43.65,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Rikko is lonely without you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.60,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, all you gotta do is stop by the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.49,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going back there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.84,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:53.64,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.32,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:03.25,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard a loud noise \N coming from here a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.66,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:06.37,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:10.73,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I wanted to give you this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.81,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:14.38,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's from our old housekeeper, Shizu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.71,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Shizu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:17.36,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:21.21,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She wrote about your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:26.92,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We've had our problems over the years,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:30.67,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems Shizu-san happened to run into your mother in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:35.40,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She got your mother's address \N and insisted I pass it on to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.83,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We split up when you were still little,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:42.18,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,so you might not remember your mom very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:46.08,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But if you'd like to go see her, you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:48.16,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe on your next break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:52.45,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is sudden and may leave you at a loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:54.79,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,but whether you go or not is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.81,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll let you get back to your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:03.14,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.54,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Give her some sweet rice treats as a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.34,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I never said I was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:10.80,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're not goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:14.75,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm just not up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:16.11,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.94,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You know where she is {\i1}now{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:20.65,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose this chance, \Nyou'll regret it for the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:26.91,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.35,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.33,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:31.50,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.88,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.28,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-kun, you're hiding something, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:46.72,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:51.97,ED-Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\bord0\shad0\frz10.785\fscx47.5\fscy60\pos(347,128)\c&H000000&\b1}TRAIN TICKET UPPER CLASS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:54.99,ED-Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\bord0\shad0\frz10.785\fscx47.5\fscy60\pos(347,128)\c&H000000&\b1}TRAIN TICKET UPPER CLASS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.52,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Blue trains?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:02.89,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,"Blue trains" basically refers to \N limited express trains from Asakaze
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:06.47,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,that have dedicated blue sleeper cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.93,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that the design of the front and back car are different
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.13,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,because they have to switch off being the lead car?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:14.90,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:25.07,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it, this is my first time traveling alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:30.02,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it like a trip to help me get over my heartache?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:31.59,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.74,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:36.63,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, it's a good thing I asked Maruo to get me a ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.07,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:41.46,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like takin' a trip to Tokyo too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.65,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm taggin' along!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:53.45,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only went on this trip to be \N alone and think things over quietly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:57.75,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Man, travel an' frozen Mandarins \N go together like bread an' butter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:00.41,Default,Old Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I do have one more Mandarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.10,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, much obliged!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:04.62,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,They taste better before they thaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.67,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn that Maruo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.71,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how can you afford this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.71,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I had money saved up from my part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.47,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,And then I sold some old records.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:21.27,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have nearly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:25.39,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I can make it to Jun-nii's place, I'm sure it'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:28.61,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a thoughtless fool.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:35.20,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is yours, Bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:39.20,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Rikko said the food in the dining car is probably expensive,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.04,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,so she made these for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:46.87,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't you gonna eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.71,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,She's been worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.28,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all these people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:19.36,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.39,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Or a New Year's sale?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.87,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo Station is always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:26.29,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go sightseeing around Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:30.41,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see what your mom's like, so I'm comin' with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.42,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\i1\shad0\bord1\b1\fscx86.25\fscy100\pos(629,59)\c&H332F29&\3c&H332F29&}BLUE BUTTERFLY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.42,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\i1\shad0\bord0\c&H749281&\b1\fscx86.25\fscy100\pos(628,56)}BLUE BUTTERFLY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.42,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\shad0\bord1\b1\fscx72.5\fscy91.25\pos(372,181)\c&H332F29&\3c&H332F29&}COUNTRY OF DREAMS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.42,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\shad0\bord0\b1\c&H858172&\fscx72.5\fscy91.25\pos(371,178)}COUNTRY OF DREAMS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.42,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\blur1\shad0\b1\fscx72.5\fscy91.25\pos(946,181)\c&H332F29&\3c&H332F29&}ESTABLISHED IN 1932
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.42,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\shad0\bord0\b1\c&H858172&\fscx72.5\fscy91.25\pos(945,178)}ESTABLISHED IN 1932
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.42,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:39.63,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This is some workplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:42.05,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, maybe I got the address wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:44.93,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.79,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go in an' ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.10,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:52.56,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed my mind about meeting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:53.81,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:56.10,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You can't quit now that you've come this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.62,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if I don't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.32,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.42,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:14.04,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,She says it's your mom's day off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.65,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'd meet you here tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.17,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll come back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:23.30,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I say we relax a bit at Jun-nii's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:32.58,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two have business with Katsuragi Junichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:33.91,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.93,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no point in waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:38.32,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,He's been missing since last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.44,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.23,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:43.86,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it he got in bad with some faction,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:46.27,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,and now he's in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:50.72,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's possible he's just shacking up with some girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:53.64,ED-English,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\shad0\bord0\b1\c&H000000&\fscx73.75\fscy66.25\frz41.256\pos(590,310)}Fukahori Yurika
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:53.64,ED-English,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\shad0\bord0\b1\c&H000000&\frz72.574\fscx63.75\fscy67.5\pos(987,467)}Fukahori Yurika
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:53.64,ED-English,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\shad0\bord0\b1\c&H000000&\fscx73.75\fscy66.25\frz69.304\pos(821,449)\clip(m 789 455 l 816 430 836 413 853 400 791 560 741 539)}Fukahori Yurika
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.64,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's popular with college girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:57.03,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no surprise if it's Jun-nii.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:58.65,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Bon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:14:59.65,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:04.33,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Have you two come all the way from Kyushu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:12.36,Default,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's make our guests from faraway Kyushu feel welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.50,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,With shochu and water...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.23,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:18.91,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:19.84,Default,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:26.65,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.41,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't believe how stupid this guy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.92,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He's always causing trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:36.31,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with him, his stupidity rubs off on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.79,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.27,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky to have such a good buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:43.55,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Buddy? Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:45.21,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Sure sounds like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.28,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare to find a friend you can get goofy with.{shorten if possible}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:49.75,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:53.89,Default,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike love affairs, friendship is for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:17.78,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:20.89,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, that is you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.25,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:25.32,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What are you standing around like a scarecrow for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.73,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:28.55,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.71,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:35.20,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:38.93,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I've never eaten fancy curry like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:42.03,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, don't be shy. Just eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.28,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:43.96,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:46.29,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I like the way you shovel it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:49.69,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a thing for men with a hearty appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:54.72,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She isn't at all the way I imagined her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:16:58.60,Default,Kaoru and Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:02.33,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:04.37,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Mother and son perfectly in unison!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.65,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:09.05,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... He has no manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.77,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Are you friends from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:11.75,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.87,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Or more like, we play music together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.98,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He's a drummer and I play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:18.89,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:22.94,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kaoru, you used to love it when your dad played the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:27.14,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He would play and I'd sing along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:31.90,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,And then, even if you were crying, you'd always stop and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.49,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:36.07,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a happy memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:38.34,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.78,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:44.59,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dad never likes to talk about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.48,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:50.79,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Who would want to talk about a washout of a mother like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.90,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the rain has stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:59.06,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm gonna take a little stroll around Ginza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.25,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I think he wanted to give us some time alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:05.64,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But eat before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:22.20,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's this curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.94,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's spicier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:28.42,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:31.54,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how's school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.42,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.61,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a girl that you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.98,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did it not work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.76,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:42.77,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not talk about that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:45.38,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What? I'm right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:47.49,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:50.51,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just the idea of the baby boy in my memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:53.27,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,who'd say "Mama" and make gurgling noises,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.66,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,having a broken heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:57.03,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the heyday of your youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.49,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,A broken heart! Not bad, not bad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:09.72,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I'm lovelorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:14.07,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The more I laughed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:16.78,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the more whatever had been building up inside me disappeared into thin air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:19.99,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My mind emptied out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.38,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.28,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you weren't gonna make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:31.40,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.18,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.69,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a jazz record.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.20,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The song called "Lullaby of Birdland."
